# UniSkill V2.2

Universal Skill Framework - Convergence Detection + Socratic Questioning + Jinja2 Templates

## Quick Start

```python
from core_v2.x_styler_v2 import XStylerV2

styler = XStylerV2()
html = styler.render_decision_card(convergence=0.85, model="qwen3.5-plus", intent="task", content="result")
```

